text: Kausea Natano (born 5 July 1957) is a Tuvaluan politician. He was the Prime Minister of Tuvalu from 19 September 2019 until 26 February 2024. He was also serving as an MP for Funafuti until 2024. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Tuvalu Category:1957 births Category:Current national leaders Category:University of the South Pacific alumni
